OL,3,CMore fare dodgers caught in London
OL,4,Cduring crackdown
OL,6,FA crackdown on fare dodging on
OL,7,FLondon's public transport network has
OL,8,Fled to a surge in the number of
OL,9,Fpassengers handed #100 penalty fares,
OL,10,Ffigures show.
OL,12,FTransport for London (TfL) said 69,001
OL,13,Fpenalty fares were issued in the year
OL,14,Fto the end of March.
OL,16,FThat is up 9% from the previous 12
OL,17,Fmonths.
OL,19,FPenalty fares are #100, reduced to #50
OL,20,Fif paid within 21 days.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/6
