OL,3,CMore fare dodgers caught in London
OL,4,Cduring crackdown
OL,6,FA further 21,533 cases resulted in
OL,7,Freports for possible prosecution, up
OL,8,F19% year-on-year.
OL,10,FTfL said 6.9 million contactless
OL,11,Fpayment cards were checked over the 12-
OL,12,Fmonth period, which represents a 51%
OL,13,Fincrease.
OL,15,FThe transport body said it secured
OL,16,F14,406 convictions for fare evasion in
OL,17,F2025/26, which was 955 more than a
OL,18,Fyear earlier.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/6
