OL,3,CMore fare dodgers caught in London
OL,4,Cduring crackdown
OL,6,FIn a recent case, a person was
OL,7,Fconvicted after being found using a
OL,8,Fbank card banned by TfL because of
OL,9,Fprevious breaches of its conditions of
OL,10,Fuse.
OL,12,FThey admitted 181 offences and were
OL,13,Fordered to pay #2,131.
OL,15,FSubscribe for free to our weekly
OL,16,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,17,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,18,Finbox every Friday morning.
