OL,3,CMore fare dodgers caught in London
OL,4,Cduring crackdown
OL,6,FTfL said 3.5% of passengers across its
OL,7,Fnetwork evade fares, which is
OL,8,F"significantly lower than many cities
OL,9,Fglobally".
OL,11,FIt is aiming to slash the figure to
OL,12,F1.5% by 2030/31.
OL,14,FSiwan Hayward, TfL's director of
OL,15,Fsecurity, policing and enforcement,
OL,16,Fsaid: "The overwhelming majority of
OL,17,Fcustomers pay the correct fare, and
OL,18,Fit's unfair that a minority avoid
OL,19,Fpaying.
OL,26,@pD@AOUqD@IO]xD@GOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/6
