CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781115078
OL,3,CMore fare dodgers caught in London
OL,4,Cduring crackdown
OL,6,F"That's why we are strengthening our
OL,7,Fcapability to detect and deter fare
OL,8,Fevasion, as shown by the significant
OL,9,Fincreases in enforcement activity
OL,10,Facross our network ` from more
OL,11,Fcustomer ticket checks to more
OL,12,Fofficers on the ground and higher
OL,13,Flevels of revenue recovered.
OL,15,F"Fare evasion is not a victimless
OL,16,Fcrime. It robs Londoners of vital
OL,17,Finvestment in a safe, frequent and
OL,18,Freliable transport network.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/6
