OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F405A1781115078
OL,3,CMore fare dodgers caught in London
OL,4,Cduring crackdown
OL,6,F"We are committed to ensuring that
OL,7,Fthose who evade fares face the
OL,8,Fconsequences of their actions, and
OL,9,Fthat the cost of fare evasion is paid
OL,10,Fby the evaders, not our fare-paying
OL,11,Fcustomers."
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@KO]
